{"tid":2530934,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"依個世界，將來會係中國人定非洲人統治？","createTime":"2021-05-14T21:35:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-14T21:43:08.000Z","uid":87072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"241d02ede779b7dda517f911d977c55a5e9def22","tid":2530934,"uid":87072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T21:35:36.000Z","msg":"中國就藉著經濟力量入侵世界，不斷增強國際既影響力，使得大如世衛淪為中國既鷹犬，小則外國品牌藝人向中國獻媚示好，埋沒良心。<br />\n<br />\n非洲人就得益於歐美左膠思想盛行，站係道德高地瘋狂攞著數，變相剝奪白人利益，從民生、文化方面大舉入侵，加上黑人生育率高，此消彼長下，法國已變成黑人國家，相信其他歐美諸國亦只有逐步步其後塵。"},{"pid":"416b3a24d8c5e665c6a5c71cf893d01c04724b1f","tid":2530934,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T21:43:08.000Z","msg":"將會係連登仔統治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為連登仔會殺晒呢2類人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/scheme.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}